The paper proposes a network for generating object proposals and improving object detection, which are tasks related to computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed network also uses a map attention decision unit to adaptively activate feature maps, which involves machine learning (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also discusses the placement of anchors and the use of feature map streams, which are related to robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM) applications.
